  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You cover your hand with neon lightning up the area around you, before quickly striking a creature within range. Make a Melee Ninjutsu Attack against a creature within range. On a hit, the target takes 3d6+3 lightning damage and the target creature sheds bright light in a 20-foot radius and dim light for an additional 20 feet for 1d4 rounds. The light can be colored as you like</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, the damage by 2d6+2 and die which determines the number of rounds the target is lit increases by 1 step. (1d4&gt;1d6&gt; 1d8&gt;1d10&gt;1d12)</p>",
